::FZ/DevilDuer::

There was no way he was going to live through this one, FZ realises as he feels Nemesis' gun press against his back. He decides to take the chance and dives toward the door just as DevilDuer walks in the room. The two bots fall out of the room.

"Out of my way!" FZ says and shoots DevilDuer, running off down a corridor.

"Damn bastard," DevilDuer swears under his breath and runs after FZ.
